{"tid":805973,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【食屎公屋仔👊🏻】公屋客掃第一城兩伙變銀主盤","createTime":"2018-09-04T09:39:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T10:27:04.000Z","uid":13663,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9d8816263fcf3d6afb7bb4c6b103f18bddd8773f","tid":805973,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:39:30.000Z","msg":"美聯物業翁凱傑表示，沙田第一城連錄兩宗成交後，亦連環出現兩間銀主盤放售。包括50座中層B室及47座高層D室，實用面積284方呎及304方呎，分別由星展及大新銀行接管，開價550萬及580萬元，呎價19,366元及19,079元。土地註冊處資料顯示，兩單位均由同一間公司持有，公司董事報住深水埗公屋南昌邨，兩單位分別於2010年及2013年購入，47座單位買入價175萬，50座單位買入價315萬元。<br />\n<br />\n土地註冊處資料顯示，47座單位今年4月曾以535萬元售出，疑拖欠代理佣金惹上官司被釘契，而該宗交易至今仍未有進展。<br />\n<br />\n記者:朱連峰"},{"pid":"66f10eac6432c855369b7b57be423b3e22a551d2","tid":805973,"uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:40:32.000Z","msg":"出現銀主盤 感覺唔對路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06ffefc7347ed84ddc03be117720619411253d5","tid":805973,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:42:08.000Z","msg":"不過放心 CCL仲係未有跌既空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baebb10f388378c69a007e90636442b458361a75","tid":805973,"uid":182286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:59:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e1e22fc5e3555393ce47449df9ca007efc0a9cb","tid":805973,"uid":39326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66f10eac6432c855369b7b57be423b3e22a551d2","tid":805973,"uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:40:32.000Z","msg":"出現銀主盤 感覺唔對路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T10:02:27.000Z","msg":"銀主盤都19K尺"},{"pid":"1ec147b30b1dcd4eb1956ba69fefc6ad58d5855a","tid":805973,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e1e22fc5e3555393ce47449df9ca007efc0a9cb","tid":805973,"uid":39326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66f10eac6432c85